snippet.title: Temtem - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Kickstarter on May 29th

Temtem is a massively multiplayer creature-collection adventure inspired by Pokémon. Seek adventure at the lovely Airborne Archipelago along your Temtem squad. Catch every Temtem, battle other tamers, customize your house, join a friend's adventure or explore the online living-world.

Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/Temtem
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/PlayTemtem/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayTemtem
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PlayTemtem/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/PlayTemtem/
